To create a new hip component follow these steps:

1. First ask if there is some docs for a headless component to look at
1. create a component in packages/hip-ui/src/components
1. Create a config for that component
1. Write it's config in the new component's dir
1. Add the config to packages/hip-ui/src/cli/install
1. Run the build
1. Run `pnpm hip install --all` in the apps/docs dir
1. Generate and .mdx page with example in apps/docs

## Rules

- Prefer using packages/hip-ui/src/components/flex and packages/hip-ui/src/components/grid over css
- Use icon from lucide-react
